or":[{"version":"red","text":"When several of these POK\u00e9MON gather, their electricity could build and cause lightning storms."},{"version":"blue","text":"When several of these POK\u00e9MON gather, their electricity could build and cause lightning storms."},{"version":"yellow","text":"It keeps its tail raised to monitor its surroundings. If you yank its tail, it will try to bite you."},{"version":"gold","text":"This intelligent POK\u00e9MON roasts hard BERRIES with electricity to make them tender enough to eat."},{"version":"silver","text":"It raises its tail to check its sur\u00ad roundings. The tail is sometimes struck by light\u00ad ning in this pose."},{"version":"crystal","text":"When it is anger\u00ad ed, it immediately discharges the energy stored in the pouches in its cheeks."},{"version":"ruby","text":"Whenever PIKACHU comes across something new, it blasts it with a jolt of electricity. If you come across a blackened berry, it\u2019s evidence that this POK\u00e9MON mistook the intensity of its charge."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"This POK\u00e9MON has electricity-storing pouches on its cheeks. These appear to become electrically charged during the night while PIKACHU sleeps. It occasionally discharges electricity when it is dozy after waking up."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It stores electricity in the electric sacs on its cheeks. When it releases pent-up energy in a burst, the electric power is equal to a lightning bolt."},{"version":"firered","text":"It has small electric sacs on both its cheeks. If threatened, it looses electric charges from the sacs."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"When several of these POK\u00e9MON gather, their electricity can build and cause lightning storms."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It lives in forests with others. It stores electricity in the pouches on its cheeks."},{"version":"pearl","text":"If it looses crackling power from the electric pouches on its cheeks, it is being wary."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It occasionally uses an electric shock to recharge a fellow PIKACHU that is in a weakened state."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"This intelligent Pok\u00e9mon roasts hard berries with electricity to make them tender enough to eat."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It raises its tail to check its surroundings. The tail is sometimes struck by lightning in this pose."},{"version":"black","text":"It occasionally uses an electric shock to recharge a fellow Pikachu that is in a weakened state."},{"version":"white","text":"It occasionally uses an electric shock to recharge a fellow Pikachu that is in a weakened state."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It occasionally uses an electric shock to recharge a fellow Pikachu that is in a weakened state."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It occasionally uses an electric shock to recharge a fellow Pikachu that is in a weakened state."},{"version":"x","text":"It raises its tail to check its surroundings. The tail is sometimes struck by lightning in this pose."},{"version":"y","text":"It has small electric sacs on both its cheeks. If threatened, it looses electric charges from the sacs."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Whenever Pikachu comes across something new, it blasts it with a jolt of electricity. If you come across a blackened berry, it\u2019s evidence that this Pok\u00e9mon mistook the intensity of its charge."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon has electricity-storing pouches on its cheeks. These appear to become electrically charged during the night while Pikachu sleeps. It occasionally discharges electricity when it is dozy after waking up."},{"version":"sun","text":"A plan was recently announced to gather many Pikachu and make an electric power plant."},{"version":"moon","text":"It\u2019s in its nature to store electricity. It feels stressed now and then if it\u2019s unable to fully discharge the electricity."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Its nature is to store up electricity. Forests where nests of Pikachu live are dangerous, since the trees are so often struck by lightning."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"While sleeping, it generates electricity in the sacs in its cheeks. If it\u2019s not getting enough sleep, it will be able to use only weak electricity."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"This forest-dwelling Pok\u00e9mon stores electricity in its cheeks, so you\u2019ll feel a tingly shock if you touch it."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"This forest-dwelling Pok\u00e9mon stores electricity in its cheeks, so you\u2019ll feel a tingly shock if you touch it."},{"version":"sword","text":"Pikachu that can generate powerful electricity have cheek sacs that are extra soft and super stretchy."},{"version":"shield","text":"When Pikachu meet, they\u2019ll touch their tails together and exchange electricity through them as a form of greeting."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Possesses cheek sacs in which it stores electricity. This clever forest-dweller roasts tough berries with an electric shock before consuming them."}],"evo":{"name":"pichu","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"pikachu","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":220,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"raichu","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"thunder-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeA